expenditureprogram

  • Classes in expenditureprogram used by expenditureprogram 
    Class Description
    Expense
    This class creates an expense that specifies the name of the expense and how much is spent on this expense every month
    ExpenseLinkedList
    This class stores all ExpenseNodes in a custom linked list and allows the Spreadsheet class to modify the linked list based on user input
    ExpenseNode
    This class stores the nodes of the ExpenseLinkedList
    Spreadsheet
    This class displays the expenses in a table, similar to a spreadsheet format
